high_descs: Turn left walk towards the refrigerator then turn right and walk towards the stove, then left and walk towards the toaster.
Pick up the knife in front of the toaster.
Take the knife, turn left, then walk towards the sink.
Slice the potato inside the sink.
Take the knife, turn all the way around facing towards the toaster.
Place the knife back in front of the toaster.
Turn back towards the sink .
Pick up a potato slice inside the sink.
Turn around facing the white table then turn right and walk towards the stove.
Place the potato slice into the microwave above the stove and cook it.
Take the potato slice out of the microwave, turn all the way around, then walk towards the sink then turn right.
Place the potato slice into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the over cooked potato slice into the sink.

high_descs: Go straight, turn left at the table, go straight to the fridge turn right, go straight, turn left at the dishwasher and face the dishwasher.
Take the knife in front of the toaster from the counter.
Go to the left to face the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Turn and face to the right.
Put the knife on the counter to the left next to the sink.
Turn left to face the sink.
Take a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn right, go straight to the oven.
Put the potato in the microwave above the oven. Cook the potato. Take the potato from the microwave.
Turn around, go straight, turn right at the sink.
Put the potato in the bottom left corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of cooked potato in a sink.

high_descs: step to the right and walk to the toaster which will be on the counter left of the sink
pick up the knife in front of the toaster
carry the knife to the sink
pause at the sink
turn around and face the stove
take the knife back to the sink
cut a slice of potato from the potato in the sink
pick up a potato slice from the sink
carry the potato slice over to the stove
cook the potato slice on the stove top
carry the cooked potato slice back to the sink
put the cooked potato slice in the sink
anns.task_desc: cook a slice of potato on the stove and place it in the sink when done

high_descs: Go forward to the table, turn left, take a step forward, turn right, go forward, turn left to the dishwasher, go forward to the dishwasher.
Take the knife from the counter above the dishwasher.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Turn to the right.
Put the knife on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn left to face the sink.
Take a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn right, go forward to the oven.
Cook the potato in the microwave above the oven.
Turn around, go forward, turn right to the sink.
Put the potato in the lower left corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in a sink.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter in front of the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left and move to in front of the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Turn left, move to in front of the dishwasher.
Put the knife on to the counter.
Turn left and move to in front of the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Put the potato slice in to the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to in front of the sink.
Put the cooked potato slice in to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of cooked potato in to the sink.
